com.quantcomponents.algo
Interface ITradingAgentExecutionManager

All Known Subinterfaces:
IStockDatabaseTradingManager, ITradingManager
public interface ITradingAgentExecutionManager

Interface to manage the execution of an algorithm All operations to create, execute, manage the execution of a trading algorithm can be performed from this interface.

See Also:
ITradingHierarchyManager
